        JOIN pg_class t ON t.oid = c.conrelid
        LEFT JOIN pg_description d ON c.oid = d.objoid
        WHERE t.relname = 'res_users' AND conname = 'res_users_notification_type';

            SELECT fk.conname, c1.relname, a1.attname, c2.relname, a2.attname, fk.confdeltype
            FROM pg_constraint AS fk
            JOIN pg_class AS c1 ON fk.conrelid = c1.oid
            JOIN pg_class AS c2 ON fk.confrelid = c2.oid
            JOIN pg_attribute AS a1 ON a1.attrelid = c1.oid AND fk.conkey[1] = a1.attnum
            JOIN pg_attribute AS a2 ON a2.attrelid = c2.oid AND fk.confkey[1] = a2.attnum

2022-04-22 12:34:22,220 87141 DEBUG test_db odoo.sql_db: query: 
            SELECT fk.conname, c1.relname, a1.attname, c2.relname, a2.attname, fk.confdeltype
            FROM pg_constraint AS fk
            JOIN pg_class AS c1 ON fk.conrelid = c1.oid
            JOIN pg_class AS c2 ON fk.confrelid = c2.oid
            JOIN pg_attribute AS a1 ON a1.attrelid = c1.oid AND fk.conkey[1] = a1.attnum

                FROM ir_ui_view
                WHERE id IN (10376) AND (("ir_ui_view"."active" = true))
            UNION

                FROM ir_ui_view

        JOIN pg_class t ON t.oid = c.conrelid
        LEFT JOIN pg_description d ON c.oid = d.objoid
        WHERE t.relname = 'res_users' AND conname = 'res_users_notification_type';

            SELECT fk.conname, c1.relname, a1.attname, c2.relname, a2.attname, fk.confdeltype
            FROM pg_constraint AS fk
            JOIN pg_class AS c1 ON fk.conrelid = c1.oid
            JOIN pg_class AS c2 ON fk.confrelid = c2.oid
            JOIN pg_attribute AS a1 ON a1.attrelid = c1.oid AND fk.conkey[1] = a1.attnum
            JOIN pg_attribute AS a2 ON a2.attrelid = c2.oid AND fk.confkey[1] = a2.attnum
            WHERE fk.contype = 'f' AND c1.relname IN ('res_company_users_rel', 'res_users', 'mail_channel_partner', 'res_groups_users_rel', 'res_partner_res_partner_category_rel', 'res_partner')

                FROM ir_ui_view
